# 🧠 Smart Data Analyst

An AI-powered data analysis web app built with Streamlit and Gemini API.  
Upload any CSV or Excel file and instantly get KPIs, charts, insights, and a downloadable report.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 **[Try it here](https://smart-data-analyst-ahkz32vjd6dzvhmexkrhdm.streamlit.app/)**

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 📂 **File Upload** | CSV and Excel (.xlsx, .xls) support |
| 📊 **Auto Dashboard** | KPI cards + charts auto-generated from your data |
| 💬 **Chat with Data** | Ask questions in plain English — get instant answers |
| 🤖 **AI-Powered** | Gemini API (primary) + Ollama local (fallback) |
| 🐍 **Python Compute** | Accurate answers via Pandas — not just LLM guesses |
| 📈 **Smart Charts** | Auto chart type selection (bar, line, pie, scatter) |
| 📥 **PDF Report** | Download full report with KPIs, charts, and Q&A |
| 📊 **Excel Report** | Multi-sheet Excel with raw data, stats, and chat history |
| 🧠 **RAG Memory** | Remembers past Q&As for better context |
| 💾 **Chat History** | Persists across sessions per dataset |

---

